# Clasp — Phased Implementation Plan

> **Philosophy**: Each phase must be fully working and tested before starting the next.
> A phase is NOT done until its DoD (Definition of Done) test passes.

---

## Overview

```
Phase 0 → Scaffold + Vendor Copy           (no logic yet, just structure)
Phase 1 → Core Engine                      (M1: "It learns")
Phase 2 → Data Ingestion (TEP Simulator)   (M1 verified end-to-end)
Phase 3 → Domain Agents                    (M2: "It explains" + M3: "It warns")
Phase 4 → FastAPI Backend                  (M4 backend half)
Phase 5 → React Dashboard                  (M4 full: "Someone can see it")
Phase 6 → OPC-UA Connector                 (M5: "A real plant can use it")
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **We only start a phase when the previous phase's DoD is green.**
> This is non-negotiable. The fastest way to break Clasp is to add agents before the engine is solid.

