### TEP column mapping

The `.dat` files are space-separated with no header. Column order:
- Columns 0–40: XMEAS(1) through XMEAS(41)
- Columns 41–52: XMV(1) through XMV(12)
- Column 53: time (hours)

The simulator maps `col_index → node_id` using a static dict defined in `tep_simulator.py`.

